# Mermaid diagrams

You can include [Mermaid](https://mermaid.js.org) diagrams using a ```` ```mermaid```` code fence.

Example input:

````djot
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Parse(Read documents) --> Read(Read pass)
    Read --> Write(Write pass)
    Write -->|If configured| Read
    Write --> Output
```
````

Example output:

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Parse(Read documents) --> Read(Read pass)
    Read --> Write(Write pass)
    Write -->|If configured| Read
    Write --> Output
```